 Documentation/gitcvs-migration.txt                 |    7 ++++-
 Documentation/gitglossary.txt                      |   25 +++++++++++++++++++
 Documentation/gittutorial-2.txt                    |    8 ++++--
 Documentation/gittutorial.txt                      |    2 +
 .../{glossary.txt => glossary-content.txt}         |    3 --
 Documentation/user-manual.txt                      |    5 +++-
